You can use a 'list' for this:

counts=c(4,6,10);

p=1;
smat <- list()
for (i in 1:length(counts))
{

   smat[[i]] <- bmat[p:p+i-1,];
   p=p+i;
}




On 6/23/07, suman Duvvuru <duvvuru.suman@gmail.com> wrote:
